(29948, 'Zincosafe 11 mg 100 caps.', 'زنكوسيف 11مجم 100 كبسولة', '34', '50', 'Zinc', 'Safe pharma', 'Cap', 'كبسولة', 'كريم مرطب للجلد', 'Zinc supplement', '11 mg', 'Zinc can be used for the treatment and prevention of zinc deficiency/its consequences, including stunted growth and acute diarrhea in children, and slowed wound healing. It is also utilized for boosting the immune system, treating the common cold and recurrent ear infections, as well as preventing lower respiratory tract infections [L2172].', '', '', 2125, '2023-04-18', CURRENT_TIMESTAMP),
